Customer Privacy Policy
Last updated on November 27, 2024
GENERAL
Burger King Europe GmbH, Dammstrasse 23, 6300 Zug, Switzerland (hereinafter BURGER KING®) collects,
                processes
                and uses personal data in accordance with the statutory provisions. In doing so, BURGER KING® respects
                the
                personal rights of its customers and other persons that visit BURGER KING® websites and mobile
                applications
                and knows the importance of protecting personal data. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. This
                Privacy
                Policy sets out how BURGER KING® (i) collects your personal data when you visit BURGER KING® websites
                and
                mobile applications, (ii) processes it for certain purposes, and (iii) shares it with third parties, as
                described in this Privacy Policy.
NAME AND ADDRESS OF THE PERSON RESPONSIBLE FOR PROCESSING
The person responsible within the meaning of the data protection laws applicable in Ireland (i.e. the
            ‘controller’ of the processing of the personal data) and who you can contact is:
