WHICH DATA IS COLLECTED AND HOW IS IT USED?
BURGER KING® collects personal data such as:
Identification information, including first name, surname, date of birth andinformation that you to
                supply to verify your identity; and
Contact information, including postal delivery address, email address, phone number, only (i) insofar as
                these are provided by you on a voluntary basis and (ii) to the extent such a collection is permitted by
                law or covered by your consent. The same applies to the transmission to BURGER KING® of personal data
                that you enter into any BURGER KING® website or mobile application, such as:
- Transaction and order information, including product purchase, order history, price, method of
                payment, points earned in any reward or promotion program, preferred restaurant locations, and payment
                details;
- Account information, including username, promotion history and other personal information or login
                credential to use the BURGER KING® websites and mobile applications.
The above mentioned personal data may be provided by you to BURGER KING® during an order or a purchase
                of a product via the BURGER KING® websites and online applications, when registering to use the BURGER
                KING® websites and online application, when requesting to receive newsletters and other marketing
                materials, promotion scheme, or communications from BURGER KING® or when submitting information in a
                feedback form, for example (Other information).
BURGER KING® also collects information on your online behaviour and preferences from your computer
                system or mobile or smart device via automated techniques when you visit BURGER KING® websites or mobile
                applications, including through cookies or other tracking technology such as web beacons (Cookie
                information). You can find additional information regarding the use of cookies and tracking technology
                below in this Privacy Policy and in our
Cookies & Tracking Policy.
